Step 1: Clone this source code (from docker Linux enviroment)
Step 2: Build the source code: 
        command:   install .
Step 3: Install npm:
        command:   sudo apt install npm
Step 4: Install nodemon
        command:   sudo apt install nodemon
Step 5: Start system with
        command:   nodemon server.js
Step 6: Change the source code with intentional idea
